  <brief_title>Chronic Administration of Diosmectite (SMECTA®) in Subjects With Chronic Diarrhoea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Elemental Impurities Level After Chronic Administration of Diosmectite (SMECTA®) in Subjects With Chronic Diarrhoea</official_title>
  <sponsors>
